libnginx-mod-http-host-normalize (1.0.0) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Normalize Host header when absolute URI is used in request line
  * Implements RFC 9112 Section 3.2.2 compliance
  * Fixes security issue with Host header spoofing

